  title: You ran into some people
  fullText: 'Their clothes look odd. You glance some northern features in their faces,
    maybe their are from Gracoy. Surely, with everything that it is going on in the
    continent they wouldn''t...

    oh no, they are coming your way. With weapons.
    They are bandits

    What will you do?'
